<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>The <span class="title-main">Statistics </span>minor consists of five upper division level courses focusing on the fundamentals of mathematical statistics and of the most widely used applied statistical methods. The minor is flexible, so that students from most majors can find a path to the minor that serves their needs.</p>
